Title: Super Milo
Plot: Determined to get over Lisa once and for all, Milo revives an intense competition that once almost destroyed the guys' friendship. But he is soon forced to make a big decision when Lisa comes back into his life. And Neal struggles to prove that he's on a par with the rest of the guys.
ParentalRatingReason: M Offensive language and sexual references
GuestStars: Meredith Hagner, Amy Smart, Joel David Moore
